[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0762","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0762.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0508","title":"开源路由器 默认口令 本地安全漏洞","description":"开源路由器、防火墙及其他网络设备上存在账户使用默认密码、空密码或未设置密码的安全漏洞。攻击者若能够通过网络连接到这些设备，即可直接利用这些弱口令或空口令登录系统，无需身份验证即可获得设备管理权限。该漏洞影响各类开源路由器及防火墙设备，CVSS 评分为 4.6，危害等级为中等。攻击者成功利用后可能导致设备配置被篡改、网络流量被劫持或设备被用于发起进一步攻击，建议管理员为所有账户设置强密码并定期更换。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0508"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:32.663","remediation":"登录路由器或防火墙管理界面，修改所有默认/空/弱密码为符合复杂度要求的高强度密码，禁用或删除不必要的默认账户，并启用账户锁定策略以防范暴力破解。如设备已停止更新，建议升级至厂商支持的最新固件版本，或在管理接口前部署访问控制列表(ACL)限制仅可信网络可达。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0508","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c271719fd48dcc28619dc324e441b822d7b4bace/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0508.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0508","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/968abdc74763b43a3cdd216fbb1950cab484f982/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0508.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/1e2d061a60b9c6823d20cc72e51f709fadad54d2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0508.json","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/d9905eb7656178d3e59e0bf8f1d53a9ee9e50186/unittests/scans/openvas/many_vuln.xml","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/cisco_no_pw.nasl","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/cve_2_MSF_exploit_Mapping/msf_module_result/msf_module_cve.txt","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/DDI_WhatsUp_Default.nasl","https://github.com/openctibr/threatFeeds/blob/3455d6adfb8ec0cc7fbb444ace396770ca5ca6c0/ExploitableVulnerabilitiesFeed.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0762.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0751","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0751.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0501","title":"Unix 账号弱口令漏洞","description":"Unix 系统账户存在可被猜测的弱口令漏洞。系统管理员或用户在创建账户时未设置足够复杂的密码（如空密码、默认密码或字典单词），导致攻击者可通过暴力破解、字典攻击或在线密码猜测等方式，在本地或远程登录场景下利用弱口令成功登录目标系统，获得未授权的 shell 访问权限。该漏洞影响所有 Unix 及类 Unix 操作系统（包括 Linux、BSD、Solaris 等），CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。修复建议为实施强密码策略和账户锁定机制。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0501"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:31.853","remediation":"在 /etc/pam.d/ 中配置 pam_cracklib.so 或 pam_pwquality.so 强制密码长度≥8位、含大小写字母和数字，并设置密码有效期≤90天；使用 `passwd -l` 锁定无密码账户，定期用 John the Ripper 审计弱口令；禁用不安全的 DES 加密，改用 SHA-512 密码哈希（`pwconv` 配合 `authconfig` 配置）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0501"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0751.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0544","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0544.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0329","title":"SGI IRIX mediad 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 操作系统中的 mediad（媒体设备管理守护进程）存在权限处理缺陷，本地普通用户可利用该程序的不当权限提升机制，通过执行特制命令或传递恶意参数，绕过系统安全检查，从而获取 root 最高权限。该漏洞影响 SGI IRIX 系统，攻击者需拥有本地 shell 访问权限，CVSS 评分为 7.2，危害等级较高。SGI 已于 1998 年 6 月发布安全公告并提供补丁修复。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0329"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:09.950","remediation":"立即安装 SGI 安全公告 19980602-01-PX 对应补丁，更新 mediad 程序至最新版本。如无法打补丁，临时缓解措施为：以 root 权限执行 `chmod -s /usr/sbin/mediad` 移除该程序的 setuid 位，阻断提权路径。考虑到 SGI IRIX 已停止官方支持，建议迁移至现代受支持操作系统以彻底消除风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":[],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0544.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0464","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0464.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0278","title":"Microsoft IIS 及 Personal Web Server ASP 源码泄露漏洞","description":"[id]\nave_id = \"AVE-1999-00001\"\naliases = [\"CVE-1999-0278\"]\n\n[basic]\ntitle = \"Microsoft IIS 及 Personal Web Server ASP 备用数据流源码泄露漏洞\"\ndescription = \"Microsoft IIS 3.0/4.0 及 Personal Web Server 2.0/3.0/4.0 存在安全漏洞，远程攻击者通过在 URL 后附加 \\\"::$DATA\\\" 可获取 ASP 文件的源代码。该漏洞利用了 Windows NTFS 文件系统的备用数据流（ADS）特性，导致服务器将 ASP 文件以文本形式返回而非执行，从而泄露数据库连接字符串、业务逻辑等敏感信息。攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，影响范围广泛。\"\nseverity = \"MEDIUM\"\nscore = 5.0\nsources = [\"cve\", \"exploitdb\"]\npublished = \"1999-01-01\"\nupdated = \"1999-01-01\"\nremediation = \"升级到 IIS 5.0 或更高版本，或安装微软提供的安全补丁。对于无法升级的系统，建议在 IIS 中配置 URL 重写规则过滤 \\\"::$DATA\\\" 请求，或迁移 ASP 应用至更新的服务器平台。\"\n\n[references]\nurls = [\"https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0278\", \"https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19033\"]\n\n[exploit]\npoc_urls = [\"https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19033\"]\nexp_urls = []\n\n[meta]\nstatus = \"completed\"\ncollected_at = \"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z\"\n\n[info]\nid = \"POC-AVE-1999-00001\"\nname = \"CVE-1999-0278 PoC\"\nauthor = \"AVE\"\nseverity = \"medium\"\ntags = [\"cve-1999-0278\", \"iis\", \"asp\", \"information-disclosure\"]\ndescription = \"检测 Microsoft IIS 是否受 ASP 备用数据流源码泄露漏洞影响，通过附加 ::$DATA 路径后缀尝试获取 ASP 源码\"\nvuln_id = [\"CVE-1999-0278\", \"AVE-1999-00001\"]\n\n[poc]\nlogic = \"any\"\n\n[[poc.requests]]\nprotocol = \"http\"\nmethod = \"GET\"\npath = \"/{{BaseURL}}/somefile.asp::$DATA\"\nheaders = { \"User-Agent\" = \"AVE/1.0\" }\n\n[[poc.requests.matchers]]\ntype = \"word\"\nwords = [\"<%\", \"Language=\", \"Response.\"]\nexpect = true\n\n[[poc.requests.extractors]]\ntype = \"regex\"\npart = \"body\"\nname = \"asp_source\"\nregex = [\"(<%.*?%>)\"]\ngroup = 1","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0278"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:03.587","remediation":"tags.\n\nActually, wait - the skill says \"输出格式铁律：下文所有 TOML、PoC、EXP 输出必须且仅包含纯 TOML 文本，不得包裹在 ``` 代码块中\". But the user's message says to put the final answer in <value> tags. So I should put the TOML inside <value> tags without ``` code blocks.\n\nLet me also think about whether I need to provide PoC/EXP TOML files separately. The skill says:\n- 写入 `output/vulns/{year}/{AVE_ID}.toml`\n- 写入 `output/pocs/{year}/POC-{AVE_ID}.toml`（如有 PoC）\n- 写入 `output/exploits/{year}/EXP-{AVE_ID}.toml`（如有 EXP）\n\nSo I need to output the main vulnerability TOML, and optionally PoC and EXP TOMLs.\n\nBut the user's message says to put the final answer in <value> tags. Let me provide all three TOML outputs inside the <value> tags.\n\nActually, re-reading the user's message: \"你可以先简要分析，但最终答案必须放在一对 <value>...","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1998/ms98-003","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A913","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19118","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0278.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0278.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0278","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0278.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0278.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9hfq-647w-q8vp/GHSA-9hfq-647w-q8vp.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0278.yaml","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-iis.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/A/asp_source_data.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0464.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0464.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0464.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1284","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1284.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1490","title":"红帽 Linux 5.1 xosview HOME 环境变量缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Red Hat Linux 5.1 中的 xosview 1.5.1 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置过长的 HOME 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，进而提升权限获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Red Hat Linux 5.1 系统中预装的 xosview 1.5.1 版本，CVSS 评分 7.2（高危），属于本地权限提升漏洞。攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，通过设置超长 HOME 环境变量并执行 xosview 程序触发缓冲区溢出，进而执行任意代码获取 root 权限。Red Hat 已发布补丁修复该漏洞，建议升级至修复版本或卸载受影响组件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1490"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-05-28T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:33.180","remediation":"建议升级 xosview 至 1.6.0 或更高版本（已修复 HOME 环境变量缓冲区溢出），或升级 Red Hat Linux 至 6.0 及以上版本。临时缓解措施：移除 xosview 的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /usr/bin/xosview），或在用户登录脚本中限制 HOME 环境变量长度（export HOME=$(echo $HOME | cut -c1-256)）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221101926021&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221101926034&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/8787.php","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/362","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19281","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/df06113bb625f86b49f1950d55874a29f8e76a55/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1490.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1490","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1490.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1490.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mvwf-xw7r-mvpr/GHSA-mvwf-xw7r-mvpr.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1490.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000302.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--edf5d74a-6f42-446c-8148-998b62a1b9cd.json","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1284.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1297","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1297.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1039","title":"SGI IRIX 6.4 补丁本地提权漏洞","description":"IRIX 操作系统在 6.4 版本的补丁 2291 和 2848 中，diskalign 与 diskperf 两个工具存在本地权限提升漏洞。由于这些工具在运行过程中会以不安全的方式创建由 root 拥有的文件，本地已登录的普通用户可借助该缺陷操纵文件创建过程，使系统生成被其控制内容的 root 属主文件，进而篡改关键系统文件或替换易受信任的二进制程序，最终达成完全获取 root 权限的本地提权。该漏洞影响安装了上述补丁的 IRIX 6.4 系统，攻击者需具备本地普通用户访问权限，通过正常调用 diskalign 或 diskperf 触发，无需远程网络即可完成利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1039"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-05-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:34.700","remediation":"从受影响补丁版本移除或降级补丁 2291 和 2848，确保 diskalign 与 diskperf 工具不再以 root 权限创建可被本地用户控制的文件；同时联系 SGI 支持获取该公告 (19980502-01-P3030) 对应的修订补丁并正确安装。若无法及时获取补丁，建议将本地用户与 root 操作严格隔离，对 diskalign 和 diskperf 的访问权限设为仅 root 可执行，并在可行情况下迁移至 IRIX 6.5 或更高版本的受支持操作系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a3a08d51f200d453300fca8b852aada6b8c5985a/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1039.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1039","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1039.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/44e56ab96b4cc04024678e20a1f15145c3b3cc59/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1039.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-79vw-mm5h-rh99/GHSA-79vw-mm5h-rh99.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1039.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000300.txt","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/db2259ea67d1f5e8ce454c4a2cee60d344017bd3/1999.tsv","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1039.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1297.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0504","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0504.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0303","title":"BNU UUCP 后台程序缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"BNU UUCP 守护进程（uucpd）在处理超长主机名时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的主机名字符串触发该漏洞，导致服务进程崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 及其他运行 BNU UUCP 组件的系统，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0303"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-05-21T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:06.610","remediation":"立即升级 OpenBSD 至 2.3 及以上版本，或安装对应安全补丁。如 UUCP 服务非必需，在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 uucpd 行并重启 inetd 服务以禁用该守护进程。同时建议在主机层面通过防火墙限制对 TCP 540 端口的访问，仅允许可信主机通信。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0303"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0504.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1330","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1330.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1096","title":"KDE kscreensaver 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"KDE 桌面环境中的 kscreensaver 屏幕保护程序（klock）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过设置超长的 HOME 环境变量，在触发屏幕锁定时导致缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 KDE 早期版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限，利用难度较低，可导致完全控制目标系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1096"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-05-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:42.810","remediation":"立即移除 kscreensaver 和 klock 二进制文件的 setuid 权限：chmod u-s /opt/kde/bin/kscreensaver /opt/kde/bin/klock。建议升级至 KDE 2.0 或更高版本，该版本已修复 HOME 环境变量缓冲区溢出问题。如无法升级，可在系统级限制本地用户设置过长的 HOME 环境变量长度作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221101925954&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221101925959&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1644","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/83494e95424aced4cfc65648b3019774f7fc51c3/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1096.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1096","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1096.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/03324c0426abad4e55ae7c73b0bba67b9c87e4ea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1096.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/799c403529fad0f67d5473eea397e9968232a5ec/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-p45q-4pfx-vgqg/GHSA-p45q-4pfx-vgqg.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83052/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1096.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idgainpre","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/20d729d7fbfed4f1ebc4b8a4255bac83c7c5af70/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1330.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1378","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1378.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1179","title":"The user wants me to generate a Chinese vulnerability title for CVE-1999-1179. The format should be \"厂商 产品 漏洞类型\" (Vendor Product Vulnerability Type). From the known information: - CVE-1999-1179 - Original title: man.sh 代码执行漏洞 - NVD description: Vulnerability in man.sh CGI script, included in May 1998 issue of SysAdmin Magazine, allows remote attackers to execute arbitrary commands. - CVSS: 7.5 (HIGH) - CWE: NVD-CWE-Other This is a CGI script called \"man.sh\" that was included in SysAdmin Magazine. It allows remote attackers to execute arbitrary commands. So the vendor could be \"SysAdmin Magazine\" or just generic, and the product is \"man.sh CGI script\" or similar. A good title following the format: \"SysAdmin Magazine man.sh CGI 远程命令执行漏洞\" or \"SysAdmin Magazine man.sh CGI 代码执行漏洞\" Let me think about what's most appropriate. The vulnerability is in the man.sh CGI script published in SysAdmin Magazine. It allows remote command execution. I'll go with something like: \"SysAdmin Magazine man.sh CGI 远程命令执行漏洞\" Actually, looking at the original title \"man.sh 代码执行漏洞\", and the","description":"man.sh CGI 脚本存在远程命令执行漏洞，该脚本随 1998 年 5 月《SysAdmin Magazine》杂志发布。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过向 Web 服务器发送特制 HTTP 请求，利用该脚本对用户输入参数过滤不严的缺陷，在目标系统上以 Web 服务器进程权限执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响配置了 man.sh CGI 脚本的各类 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议立即移除或禁用该 CGI 脚本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1179"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-05-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:53.240","remediation":"立即删除或停用服务器上的 man.sh CGI 脚本，该脚本未对用户输入进行过滤，允许远程命令执行。如仍需类似功能，应使用经过安全审计的替代实现（如 man.cgi）并确保对用户输入进行严格过滤和验证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/9330","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1179.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1179","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1179.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1179.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-j683-rf8r-r7h8/GHSA-j683-rf8r-r7h8.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1179.json","https://github.com/magicsword-io/Magic-SigExplorer/blob/2c28b91b003429a144a687199ee99ebd26f1a343/Magic-SigExplorer/docs/cve_report.md","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000298.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/dd9f81e9fd85457bf78c55783cb6a31e9af71d63/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1378.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0146","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0146.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0055","title":"Sun libnsl 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 操作系统的 libnsl（网络服务库）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，漏洞源于对 RPC 请求参数长度缺乏正确的边界检查。本地或远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送特制的 RPC 数据包触发该漏洞，成功利用后可获得系统的 root 权限，完全控制受影响主机。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.x 系列版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高危。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0055"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-05-14T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:28.320","remediation":"立即为 Sun Solaris 安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00172 对应补丁，为 AIX 系统安装 APAR IX80543 修复程序。如无法立即打补丁，可通过限制本地用户登录、移除不可信用户访问权限、对关键系统启用强制访问控制机制（如 SELinux）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-12T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/172","http://www-1.ibm.com/support/search.wss?rs=0&q=IX80543&apar=only"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0146.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1394","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1394.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1204","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9157,\"outputTokens\":23,\"totalTokens\":10844}}","description":"Check Point Firewall-1 防火墙在解析用户自定义对象时，无法正确处理 Mail、auth、time 等受限关键字。当管理员在对象定义中误用这些关键字时，防火墙会错误生成默认\"ANY\"地址的规则，导致访问范围超出管理员预期，使本应受限的网络访问被扩大，攻击者可借此访问更多受保护的内部系统。该漏洞影响使用用户自定义对象且依赖关键字配置访问规则的 Firewall-1 部署环境，攻击条件为攻击者处于被错误放宽的规则所覆盖的网络路径中，利用方式是通过触发含受限关键字的错误规则实现越权访问。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1204"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:56.473","remediation":"建议将 Check Point Firewall-1 升级至厂商已修复的版本，避免在用户定义对象名称中使用 Mail、auth、time 等受限关键字。若必须使用，请手动检查生成的规则库，将默认的 \"ANY\" 地址替换为明确指定的主机或网段，并逐条审核访问控制规则，确保未意外放行超出预期的系统访问权限。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=90221101925912&w=2","http://www.checkpoint.com/techsupport/config/keywords.html","http://www.osvdb.org/4416","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7293","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2126251525a2d370ea93bd7affc3a9b71b419b4c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1204.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1204","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1204.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d281505551869bb381f43b6d1c6cb3abf45ad885/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1204.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/5d945305f2cad48b7bb06af582393a58c31555d3/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xmpr-j5r4-rg4x/GHSA-xmpr-j5r4-rg4x.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88630/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1204.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000296.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--520b0898-fd3f-4403-9d1f-da0e40014bba.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1394.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1169","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1169.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0816","title":"摩托罗拉 CableRouter 端口 1024 远程未授权配置访问漏洞","description":"Motorola CableRouter 宽带路由器在端口 1024 上开放了未授权的管理与配置服务，任何能够访问该端口的远程用户均可直接连接并对路由器进行配置操作，无需身份认证。攻击者可利用此缺陷远程查看或修改路由器配置，甚至更改网络设置、获取管理员权限，进而控制内网流量或造成网络中断。该漏洞影响运行相关固件的 Motorola CableRouter 设备，攻击条件为攻击者能与目标设备 1024 端口建立网络连通。利用方式简单，仅需向该端口发起连接并使用其配置协议即可完成未授权操作，CVSS 评分高达 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0816"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-05-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.060","remediation":"建议立即升级 Motorola CableRouter 固件至最新版本（如官方仍提供补丁），或在防火墙层面封禁 TCP 端口 1024 的所有外部访问。若无法升级固件，请在路由器管理界面禁用远程管理功能，并将管理界面访问限制为仅信任的内网 IP 地址段访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.netspace.org/cgi-bin/wa?A2=ind9805B&L=bugtraq&P=R1621","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/df06113bb625f86b49f1950d55874a29f8e76a55/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0816.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0816","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0816.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0816.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-cjmq-x9wr-c6v6/GHSA-cjmq-x9wr-c6v6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0816.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1a48089c-6157-4609-a5eb-59d8260381a4.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--1a48089c-6157-4609-a5eb-59d8260381a4.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1169.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1302","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1302.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1044","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9115,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10797}}","description":"Digital UNIX（即 Tru64 UNIX）4.0 至 4.0d 版本中的高级文件系统工具（advfs）存在本地权限提升漏洞。该漏洞源于 advfs 实用程序在处理文件操作时对权限校验逻辑存在缺陷，导致已登录系统的本地普通用户能够利用该工具绕过正常的访问控制机制，将自身权限提升至更高等级（如 root）。攻击条件要求攻击者必须先在目标主机上获得一个合法的本地用户账户，并能够执行受影响的 advfs 相关命令；由于属于本地利用，无需网络访问即可完成。成功利用后，攻击者可完全控制受影响系统，读取、修改或删除任意文件，并执行任意系统级操作，对系统机密性、完整性和可用性构成严重威胁。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1044"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1998-05-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:35.320","remediation":"建议将 Digital UNIX（Tru64 UNIX）升级至 4.0e 或后续已修复版本，并安装厂商发布的相关补丁。如无法立即升级，应限制普通用户对 advfs 相关程序的访问权限，通过文件系统权限配置（如 chmod 去除 setuid 位）及最小权限原则降低本地提权风险，同时加强审计日志监控异常提权行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://ciac.llnl.gov/ciac/bulletins/i-050.shtml","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7431.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1044.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1044","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1044.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1044.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-74gm-9j59-cq94/GHSA-74gm-9j59-cq94.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1044.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000293.txt","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_gainpre.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1302.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0272","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0272.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0126","title":"SGI IRIX xterm 缓冲区溢出本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SGI IRIX 及 Solaris 5.5.1 X11R6.3 系统中 xterm 终端模拟器与 Xaw 部件库存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 xterm 的 `-xrm` 参数传递超长资源字符串触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用后可获得目标系统的 root 权限。该漏洞要求攻击者拥有本地账号，攻击复杂度较低，影响 SGI IRIX 和 Solaris 等 UNIX 系统的 X11R6.3 环境。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0126"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1998-05-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.733","remediation":"移除 xterm 的 SUID 权限位：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/X11/xterm`，防止本地用户通过 `-xrm` 参数以 root 权限执行任意代码。同时升级 Solaris 至 5.5.1 以上补丁版本，或从 IRIX 厂商处获取 xterm 安全修补程序。如不使用 Xaw 库程序，建议将其一并移除或降权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-010.shtml","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/338","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0126","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0126.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0126.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x84000/83078/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--160f8a79-d4d5-4c33-8fab-f1a31520e3d2.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0272.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1151","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1151.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0796","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"inputTokens\":10766,\"outputTokens\":18,\"totalTokens\":10784}}","description":"FreeBSD 操作系统实现的 T/TCP（TCP 扩展事务协议，RFC 1644）在处理事务连接时存在设计缺陷，攻击者可通过伪造源 IP 地址和 TCP 序列号构造欺骗性数据包，从而绕过正常的三次握手与连接认证机制，冒充可信主机发起事务请求。该漏洞影响启用了 T/TCP 扩展的 FreeBSD 系统，攻击条件为攻击者需能够向目标主机发送网络数据包且无需通过完整身份认证，利用方式即构造特制 T/TCP 数据包实施地址欺骗，可能导致未授权访问或会话劫持等安全风险。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0796"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1998-05-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:04.550","remediation":"升级 FreeBSD 系统到已修复该问题的版本（建议更新至 1999 年 11 月发布的 FreeBSD 3.3-STABLE 或 4.0 及以上版本，应用相关安全补丁）。如无法立即升级，可在内核中禁用 T/TCP 扩展（通过 sysctl 设置 net.inet.tcp.rfc1644=0 关闭 RFC 1644）或在前端防火墙/路由设备上过滤伪造源地址的 T/TCP 连接，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6089","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/fe807f4098db5a5ad8dcb41a479197724cb9e789/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0796.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0796","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0796.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f7f250b0cc5cc23741447612a2f182f04c36db78/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0796.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2q2r-gmfr-mh6v/GHSA-2q2r-gmfr-mh6v.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0796.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_154100_154200.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--4e8e1bc7-3f9d-4b7f-8a7c-1f1589f49db4.json","https://github.com/Ethishh/securin_assessment/blob/e6ce9197b6593ae46f3f5646d268181eea6cbb31/cve_sync.log","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/9d62a17e1fed77f73d80a5cfda0f78f06970e41d/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1151.toml"}]